Package dslabs.framework

Interface Message

All Superinterfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public interface Message
extends java.io.Serializable

Base interface for all messages in the system. You will need to create implementers of Message to define various types of messages in your system.

All messages must properly implement Object.equals(Object), Object.hashCode(), and Object.toString().
